rawQuery: q = [ from scan(public:adhoc10GB8W:lineitemHash) as c,scan(public:adhoc10GB:supplierReplicate) as d,scan(public:adhoc10GB:customerReplicate) as e,scan("public:adhoc10GB:partReplicate") as f where d.s_suppkey = c.l_suppkey and e.c_custkey = c.l_custkey and f.p_partkey = c.l_partkey and l_linenumber <= 1 and l_orderkey <= 23994434 emit c_nation,s_nation,p_mfgr,s_name,p_type,c_nation_prefix,s_nation_prefix,c_name,c_phone,s_phone]; store(q, query523);
